title: George Harrison: Living in the Material World
resume: George Harrison: Living in the Material World is a 2011 documentary film directed by Martin Scorsese, based on the life of Beatles member George Harrison. It has earned six nominations at the 64th Primetime Emmy Awards, winning Outstanding Nonfiction Special and Outstanding Directing for Nonfiction Programming.
